contentheadline.headline: List of governors of Västernorrland County

contentrichtext.text: This is a list of Governors for [[Västernorrland County]] of [[Sweden]], from 1658 to present. Västernorrland was created from the briefly existing [[Härnösand County|Härnösand]] and [[Hudiksvall County|Hudiksvall Counties]] in 1654, which in turn had been separated from [[Norrland County]] in 1645. {| style="background:transparent;" |- style="vertical-align:top;" | *[[Johan Oxenstierna, the younger|Johan Oxenstierna]] (1658-1664) *[[Gustaf Banér]] (1664) *[[Carl Larsson Sparre]]
